{"id": "1184746054814543912", "channel_id": "1184746054814543912", "type": 0, "author_id": "1020314712229027840", "author_name": "sky1324.", "author_bot": false, "content": "一测就在关注的问题，因偏深海厨就注意到了，目前法洛思的身高数据和一测一致为5'5.7\"，与对此唤醒体的故事中描述不一致，灯塔再怎样身高也不该这么点才是。多少让人想绘制群像时出现认知冲突而忽略实装数据按主观来了。\n且弥利亚姆在一测与法洛思身高是一样的。对这一块是否会进行更改而更加符合唤醒体们呢？", "timestamp": "2023-12-14T06:37:50.985000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184746054814543912", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」关于角色身高数据的疑惑", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1184880296001290270", "channel_id": "1184880296001290270", "type": 0, "author_id": "440869988505747467", "author_name": "kala_fromhk", "author_bot": false, "content": "\"折躍\"刻印的效果怎麼是刪除超維空間最右邊的的卡,抽一張牌?\n超維空間滿的時候打\"折躍\"卡還要倒扣兩張超維空間卡是什麼鬼", "timestamp": "2023-12-14T15:31:16.578000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-12-14T15:31:32.785000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1184880365182136412", "filename": "2023-12-14-23-26-11.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 18359625, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184880296001290270/1184880365182136412/2023-12-14-23-26-11.mp4?ex=6a00a4d5&is=69ff5355&hm=b214c0ed412d270364860aad21682b3c0661e62dc5e829fcc89e5908bc9c78dc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184880296001290270", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」關於\"折躍\"刻印", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1184927475701125140", "channel_id": "1184927475701125140", "type": 0, "author_id": "1180864295987322950", "author_name": "fake_view", "author_bot": false, "content": "這張卡賣出去只有30黑印，感覺有點不合理？\n還有好像是今天更新後才有的bug，經驗顯示不對勁\n最後一個疑問，相位之弈在說明裡面作為一個“附贈玩法”，把收益放在裡面是否合理？如果想作為主要玩法也請別這麼拐彎抹角……\n還有最後一個建議就是每天深潛結算有點累人，是否可以減負一點？我們這裡有討論一些解決方法。總的來說要麼減結算要麼減流程。\n具體一點大概是：深潛經驗塞到每日里去，每日任務可以累計三天，深潛还是每日一換，沒打的分數变为上一日的90%參與排名\n類似的做法？畢竟每個人不是每天都有時間打🥲", "timestamp": "2023-12-14T18:38:45.095000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1184927476149923901", "filename": "Image_1702577166403.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 95111, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184927475701125140/1184927476149923901/Image_1702577166403.jpg?ex=6a00d0b5&is=69ff7f35&hm=6ae3f0d3e6cdb3deb14ccb3a2538abdb782d5f32bd8da07ae8a2d53b13826ccb&"}, {"id": "1184927476409958581", "filename": "Screenshot_20231215_021156.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 81694, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184927475701125140/1184927476409958581/Screenshot_20231215_021156.jpg?ex=6a00d0b5&is=69ff7f35&hm=542e7733edfe308e0981617862e2fdf32a5178418732c0fffe7196c83db3d9dc&"}, {"id": "1184927476699377734", "filename": "Screenshot_20231215_020504.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 97306, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184927475701125140/1184927476699377734/Screenshot_20231215_020504.jpg?ex=6a00d0b5&is=69ff7f35&hm=07cf1fc379b727e2433e417e7d24a3485ecfc5d1dfe5e34d32b2d8248f6fe77e&"}, {"id": "1184927476951023626", "filename": "Screenshot_20231215_022247.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 97688, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184927475701125140/1184927476951023626/Screenshot_20231215_022247.jpg?ex=6a00d0b5&is=69ff7f35&hm=45681b64cfc63ce51d88d00ce13135addca27bb162a3f13c5739f0d9fd9f42a9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184927475701125140", "flags": 0, "t